title: Trip
text: Was in Paris for some days... beautiful and hughe museum... long waiting to get ticket so buy it before more better and faster.... they have a discount for students or people under 27....

title: Marriage
text: was in this hotel for couple days for a greek wedding nice and friendly people. good breakfast... all of them speak well english... near the city center.. easy reachable by bus and by taxi costs somehting about 25 euros 30 min drive

title: Alpstria
text:
We booked a transfer from Innsbruck to Lech, the driver he was really friendly experinced driver drove all the way smooth wich is difficult to drive (who makes holiday in lech could understand). We booked (2persons no ski) a eklass and was picked up with an S klass mercedes very luxury car this was a big suprising upgrade really friendly from the alpstria company, we were lucky . Definitely will choose them again even if its not a Sklass :P .... ;)
thx for the great experince for our holiday....

title: Ridicilous
text: I wanted to book a transfer from the Airport Innsbruck to Mayrhofen for my friend and me, in case of that we both was looking in the internet for a transfer for us my friend who was in the uk told me the price to mayrhofen it was showing to him more expensive than to me at the same time we was phoning on the phone and we was shocked how they could cheat on us about the prices to show in every country different prices so we booked on a other safe company who offered for us both the same price a local originaly airport taxi who is also on the innsbruck airport at the first tabella. The people who book here taxis and maybe somewhere else the prices ar unfurtunately different anyway! thats why i just can give 1 star!

title: Best Airport Transfer Tirol Innsbruck To Skiresourts
text: we booked a transfer from innsbruck Airport to our Hotel. The driver from Alpstria collect us heartful on the airport and drove us to our hotel. the transfer was just beautiful with the view to the skiresourt. thank you alpstria! thats why i give this company 5 stars and for the tip top new cars from mercedes
